reviewText: Great flick, more of a new age love and heart break flick.
One of my favorite anti-love stories of all time! Cool outtakes.
I do love this movie and finally bought it on Blu Ray. It's one of my tops favorites that I don't get sick of as well.
Came in brand new and in perfect condition.
I  loved this movie and I had to have it. It's a simple packaging with no surprises. So, expect the movie and nothing more.
One of my favorite movies! great story, production, music! all of it is great. Everytime I see it I wonder why this wasn't a huge success in theaters.
Excellent performances by the two main characters. A lot of fun and heartbreak. Thoroughly enjoyed.
Bought it for class had such high hopes for it but it didn't go well, not sure I'll ever watch it again.
This is not a love story

This is a decent movie, but there is so much better out there if you want a romantic comedy. The girl in this movie didn't feel likable at all, and was overly complicated, boring, and not cool at all. The guy was also pretty boring... It's pretty realistic though, from a man's perspective that's for sure. I would highly recommend checking out Garden State, or Midnight in Paris if you haven't seen those yet. They characters in those 2 movies have better development, and personality. Save this one for when you run out of good movies to watch.
I love this movie and this is a really great price!
Wonderful love story that's NOT a love story.
